headline.main: BROOKLYN CITY.; A UNIVERSITY FOR BROOKLYN. MORTAIITY.-

docs.lead_paragraph: A UNIVERSITY FOR BROOKLYN.--We announced some weeks since that a project was on foot establishing a University in this city. Since that time a call for a meeting to consider the subject was given in the various churches of the city, at which meeting quite a number of our most respectable citizens attended.

headline.main: WILLIAMSBURG CITY.; THE PATENT-SAFE GAME- FERRY MEETING.-- HORRIBLE SUICIDE.--

docs.lead_paragraph: THE PATENT-SAFE GAME--ARREST OF A CONFIDENCE MAN.--Another patent-safe operation was perpetrated yesterday forenoon about 11 o'clock, by which a countryman named Oliver Smith, residing in Coshocton County, Ohio, was swindled out of $200. Mr. Smith arrived in New York on Monday morning, on his way to California, and stopped at the Girard House.
